   violence following the Columbine massacre was initiated by imitation.
   Design: A database of threats of school violence reported to the
   Pennsylvania Emergency Management Agency, Harrisburg, during the 50 days
   following the Columbine incident was examined to determine the daily
   frequency of threats. To determine factors that predict the occurrence
   of these threats, counties and school districts in which threats
   occurred were noted.
